<div class="row w-100 m-0" style="overflow: hidden">
	<div id="section-main" class="sermons-col-left bg-grey" style="width:100%">
		<h1 class="color-1a8090 bg-white text-center pb-2 pt-3 h2">第85屆 奮興會 第8講</h1>
		<article class="article pt-0 p-lg-5 pt-lg-0">
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/37">費蘭度博士</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85">第85屆</a>
				</span>
				<span data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="性質">
					<i class="fa fa-folder-open"></i>
					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=85#session-master-49">奮興會</a>
				</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="article-tag">
				<a href="#" class="badge">路加福音</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">講道會</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">56屆</a>
				<a href="#" class="badge">麥希真牧師</a>
			</div>-->
			<div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
				<h2 class="article-title mb-0 h3">
					第八講  對人敏感，向神降服				</h2>
									<a type="button" class="bookmark ms-3 " data-model="app\models\SessionMessage" data-model-id="853"></a>
							</div>
						<div class="article-content">
				
				<div class="h5 mb-4 d-md-flex justify-content-lg-between align-items-center">
					<div><span>經文：</span> 哥林多前書  <a class="article-citation" href="javascript:void(0)" data-book="46" data-start-chapter="13" data-start-verse="4">13:4</a></div><div><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-danger btn-show-scripture text-center my-2 ml-auto align-self-start" style="display:none;">顯示經文</a>
				</div></div>				<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">基督徒對人要存敏銳的心，在公眾場合需要，在家庭之中更加需要。能夠敏銳而不失禮的，就是懂得尊重別人的人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">南非的曼德拉是個偉人，當上總統之後，不論何人進入他的房間，他都站起來歡迎。他的顧問很不高興，因為孟德拉對人實在太有禮貌了。所以那顧問說</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">:「其實你不用每次都站起來。」但這是他待人接物的方式。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">家庭是最需要負責任的地方，父母向小孩說話的方式，直接讓孩子瞭解自己是否有價值，他們的自我價值，是在家中塑造的。如讓他們感到自己在家中的重要性，在有需要時父母願意聆聽他們，這樣成長的小孩，就會有健全的人格。如果夫婦說話粗魯，互相態度不好，這是不快樂的家庭，在這種關係中成長的小孩子，也不會健全的。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">基督徒的愛是有決心的愛，是刻意的，不是隨便就會有的愛。所以我們在家中要作決定，決定不跟小孩子粗魯地對話，也不允許對家人說出煩躁的說話。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">雅各書</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">3:2說:「原來我們在許多事上都有過失。」當犯錯時，我們需要開口認錯。記得一個傳道人的說話令我印象深刻：在家中最難說出口的就是『我錯了，對不起』。當知道自己做錯時，一定要開口道歉。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">克服煩躁的心情，就是多安靜在主的面前。不論有多麼的忙碌，都需要用時間親近神，放慢腳步，在忙碌之中抽出半刻寧靜。如果太忙，要放棄一些事務，但不論放棄什麼，也不要放棄親近神的時間。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">愛是不堅持己見，即是不會只顧自己的想法。為別人設想，是能因別人的緣故而放棄自己的計劃。基督教常說降服，什麼是降服？就是拒絕堅持自己的權利。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">美國傳教士</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Stanley Jones提到人對慾望有三個回應：</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">第一種回應：縱慾</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">縱欲是不論好壞，想做便做。有試探的時候，不用考慮便回應了它。但這樣做就不像人了。因為聖經說，我們受造是因為聖潔。有人說</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">:「神從來不會令我完全不會犯罪，不過，祂令我不用犯罪亦能感到高興。」如果無止境地縱慾，就註定不快樂。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">第二個回應：禁慾</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">視慾望為錯誤，所以就要禁慾。但禁慾苦修，其實與人性不相符。因為聖經告訴我們，有慾望的這種機能，也是神所賜的，慾望本身並不邪惡。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">第三種回應：降服</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">對自己慾望降服，並交託給神，經過神的救贖，再歸還給我們，讓我們享受它。並不是丟棄慾望，而是要交給神作拯救，與神的美意互相結合，神有善良可喜悅的美意，所以降服不是苦差。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">我在青年歸主協會的一共工作</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">47年，人生最大的痛苦，是此機構給我的。有時我想:「不如走吧。」不過神既然派我到這裡服侍人，我也想說，人生中最大的快樂，亦是從這裡帶來。現在，我不再想痛苦的事，而是想那些快樂的事。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">不願意交出自己、不願意降服是愚蠢的。</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Stanley Jones說:「要是不向神降服，你便把自己看作神，向自己降服。」你不會喜歡你自己這個神，因為當為所欲為之時，你也不會喜歡你的所作所為。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">向神降服，不等於沒有上進心。「我們為你的緣故，終日被殺。人看我們如將宰的羊。」</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">(羅8:36)有些人讀到這經文，便害怕成為羊。但看看下一節:「在這一切的事上，已經得勝有餘了。」不但得勝，而是得勝有餘。人看到神的榮耀後，一定會有雄心大志，他的生命更能反映神的榮美。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">所以，不用放棄你的夢想，若夢想是從神而來的話，要努力去追尋。神帶領走的道路，是超過我們所求所想的，結果更加美好。降服不是打敗仗的意思，在爭戰中投降會一無所有。但基督徒向神降服，衪就救贖並恢復我們，叫我們榮神益人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">亨利馬田</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">(Henry Martyn)蒙神呼召到印度傳教。但他的女友Lydia卻不想去。</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">選去印度或是</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">Lydia？他最終選擇了印度，他在日記寫下:「親愛的Lydia與神二者是在不同的方向，但神不丟棄我。神比Lydia更加親近我，祂必不放棄我。」</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">亨利馬田翻譯了穆斯林和波斯文的聖經，但很年輕卻病死了。</span></span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">130年後，他那兩個譯本的聖經仍是很多譯本的藍本。有人把他日記編印出書，有很多人用他的日記到印度各地傳教。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin:0cm">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="margin:0cm"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:#f6f6f6"><span style="layout-grid-mode:char"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="color:black">今天，印度和美國都設有「亨利馬田的穆斯林研究中心」，亦有特別大會紀念他的宣教活動，有人稱他為英國最出色的英雄人物。這個偉人之所以出現，是因為獻上自己，向神降服。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
				
				<br>
				<p class="h5">
					<span>講員：</span> 費蘭度博士
					<br>
					<span>速記：</span> 曉明
				</p>			</div>
			<div class="article-navigation d-flex justify-content-between mt-5">
